last_episode_to_air.name: The Sound of ATL
last_episode_to_air.overview: Strip clubs can't exist without music. The soundtrack is what powers the moves and the dollars, but the kind of music to which strippers dance has changed repeatedly throughout history. Today, playing the right song can make or break a strippers night and an artists career so the visible image of strippers and the clubs are embodied in hip-hop culture.

name: Naked Hustle
overview: Naked Hustle is an in-depth look into the dark reality of exotic dancing.
